{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 300KW WAXS Detector Workflow"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 71,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os, glob, re\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from smi_analysis import SMI_beamline\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "**Helper Functions**"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 72,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def plot_2d_image(data, ax, extent=None, aspect=None):\n",
    "    ax.imshow(data,\n",
    "        vmin=np.percentile(data,1),\n",
    "        vmax=np.percentile(data,99),\n",
    "        cmap='inferno',\n",
    "        extent=extent,\n",
    "        aspect=aspect,\n",
    "        origin='upper')\n",
    "\n",
    "def get_wa(file_name):\n",
    "    match_obj = re.search(pattern='_wa(\\d+.\\d+)', string=file_name.split('/')[-1])\n",
    "\n",
    "    return float(match_obj.groups()[0])"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Collect data file names into a list"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 73,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Files Found:  ['300kw_wa0.0.tif', '300kw_wa6.5.tif', '300kw_wa13.0.tif', '300kw_wa19.5.tif', '300kw_wa26.0.tif']\n",
      "WAXS Detector Angles:  [0.0, 6.5, 13.0, 19.5, 26.0]\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "# Path to directory where data files are stored\n",
    "data_path = os.getcwd()\n",
    "\n",
    "# get all files within `data_path`\n",
    "data_files = glob.glob(data_path + '/*')\n",
    "\n",
    "# keep only file names\n",
    "data_files = [f.split('/')[-1] for f in data_files]\n",
    "\n",
    "# keep only .tif files\n",
    "data_files = [f for f in data_files if f.endswith('.tif')]\n",
    "\n",
    "# sort files by waxs detector rotation angle\n",
    "data_files.sort(key=get_wa)\n",
    "\n",
    "# make a list of all detector rotation angles\n",
    "wa_list = [get_wa(f) for f in data_files]\n",
    "\n",
    "print('Files Found: ', data_files)\n",
    "print('WAXS Detector Angles: ', wa_list)\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Define SMI Geometry"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Refer to the calibration tutorial to find `sdd` and `poni1` and `poni2`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 74,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "sdd = 273.9         # mm\n",
    "poni1 = 0.2151720   # m\n",
    "poni2 = 0.0166840   # m"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 75,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "energy = 18.1                                       # keV\n",
    "beam_center = [poni2/(172e-6), poni1/(172e-6)]      # pixels - 300kw pixel size = 172 um/px (see calibration tutorial)\n",
    "\n",
    "smi = SMI_beamline.SMI_geometry(\n",
    "    geometry='Transmission',                        # Transmission or Reflection\n",
    "    sdd=sdd,                                        # mm\n",
    "    wav=1E-10 * (12.39842/energy),                  # m\n",
    "    center=beam_center,                             # pixels\n",
    "    bs_pos=[[97, 1203]],                            # pixels - must be a list of a list and must be integer values\n",
    "    detector='Pilatus300kw',\n",
    "    det_angles=[np.deg2rad(v) for v in wa_list],    # radians\n",
    "    alphai=np.deg2rad(0)                            # radians\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# add data files to smi geometry\n",
    "smi.open_data(data_path, data_files)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Stitch Images Together"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 76,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "smi.stitching_data(interp_factor=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "plot_2d_image(smi.img_st, ax, extent=[*smi.qp, *smi.qz])\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Caking Procedure"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 77,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "smi.caking()\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots()\n",
    "aspect = abs(smi.q_cake[0]-smi.q_cake[-1]) / abs(smi.chi_cake[0] - smi.chi_cake[-1])\n",
    "extent = [smi.q_cake[0], smi.q_cake[-1], smi.chi_cake[-1], smi.chi_cake[0]]\n",
    "plot_2d_image(smi.cake, ax=ax, extent=extent, aspect=aspect)\n",
    "\n",
    "ax.axvline(.8)\n",
    "ax.axvline(2)\n",
    "ax.axhline(105)\n",
    "ax.axhline(-40)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Radial Integration"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 78,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "smi.radial_averaging(radial_range=(0.5,4))\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.plot(smi.q_rad, smi.I_rad)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('$q \\, [\\AA^{-1}]$')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Intensity')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Azimuthal Integration"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 79,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 640x480 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "smi.azimuthal_averaging(radial_range=(0.8, 2.0), azimuth_range=(-40, 105))\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.plot(smi.chi_azi, smi.I_azi)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('$\\chi \\, [deg]$')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Intensity')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  }
